{"tid":2241342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA》川普酸湖人奪冠：「只有中國人在看」","createTime":"2020-10-13T08:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T01:33:58.000Z","uid":202966,"like":94,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"877e00edb0f22ebe6c5415133ae043814d71c4f8","tid":2241342,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"洛杉磯湖人勇奪NBA總冠軍，主將詹姆斯(LeBron James)的頭號酸民換人了，現在是美國總統川普(Donald Trump)。昔日身為運動迷，川普對於湖人第17座總冠軍毫無感覺，他大病初癒後也不忘推文嗆聲。<br />\n<br />\n「NBA總冠軍賽最終戰的收視率重挫將近70%，輸給了隨便一場美式足球賽。或許都是中國人在看吧，但我不太相信。總之我毫無興趣！」大陸央視在火箭隊的香港事件後停止轉播NBA，直到湖人在總冠軍賽聽牌了(第5戰)才恢復全國轉播。<br />\n<br />\n川普的數據來自《Breitbart Sports》的分析文章，報導指出總冠軍賽G6在美國的收視人數最高峰時僅有603萬人，同日NFL維京人與海鷹隊的收視數達到1200萬人。維京人與海鷹是很無聊的對決，收視人數卻是兩倍之多。去年暴龍對勇士，那場沒有詹姆斯的總冠軍戰，最高峰有1834萬人，相較之下今年重挫66%。<br />\n<br />\n這種情況有各種解讀，湖人「大欺小」本來就不會精采，至於川普當然是一股腦推到詹姆斯、黑人民權(BLM)、香港爭議上面。無論是否政治因素，NBA總裁席爾佛(Adam Silver)已經宣告明年球季不會再使用種族平權和BLM這些圖騰，「我們明白球迷只是想看籃球而不是社會正義問題。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1315747649681870849?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1315747649681870849%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201013003030-260403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1315747649681870849%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1315747649681870849%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chinatimes.com%252Frealtimenews%252F20201013003030-260403&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c4a8b644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1315747649681870849%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1315747649681870849%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chinatimes.com%252Frealtimenews%252F20201013003030-260403&h=ddbc75f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1315747649681870849?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1315747649681870849%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201013003030-260403</a>"},{"pid":"96825962765f93fcf0e3d0b0f958ce1a3f29645c","tid":2241342,"uid":321977,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"奶共占<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fSQycV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fSQycV.jpg&h=a692dd33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M37Ufrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM37Ufrg.jpg&h=a8942ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEwmESW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEwmESW.jpg&h=094b80ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N056QZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN056QZC.jpg&h=8208d85d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cce7f0c6a1d50f5840badf7be4c92c20c35650d4","tid":2241342,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"一年跌66%"},{"pid":"0ea489fb2aa612f82adcbf8b7adeb798ecc39e6d","tid":2241342,"uid":34295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"NBA係美國係咪唔太興？"},{"pid":"e034e8e8357f067d03219a7d3bfbc6a266909550","tid":2241342,"uid":149494,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0ea489fb2aa612f82adcbf8b7adeb798ecc39e6d","tid":2241342,"uid":34295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"NBA係美國係咪唔太興？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"第三大運動<br />\n僅次美足同棒球<br />\n遠勝足球"},{"pid":"228f60a22dc19ed54427550307a9a9b22b2572d3","tid":2241342,"uid":28547,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ea489fb2aa612f82adcbf8b7adeb798ecc39e6d","tid":2241342,"uid":34295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci